Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.98,0:00:07.32,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,So we need your songs to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.32,0:00:09.23,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,heal the Star Whale's sickness!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.23,0:00:10.33,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.33,0:00:12.95,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the situation, \NI'll head there now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.95,0:00:14.49,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be okay, too, Cou-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.49,0:00:15.53,DogDays-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.53,0:00:17.07,DogDays-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,We'll head up into the sky right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.07,0:00:18.43,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.43,0:00:20.11,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,We'll come get you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.11,0:00:22.38,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,There's no time, so let's meet in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.38,0:00:23.04,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.04,0:00:23.87,DogDays-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.51,0:00:27.28,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Let's meet up with the princesses \Nand head back to the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.60,0:00:30.57,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a bad feeling somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.48,0:02:10.98,DogDays-ep-title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}Song of the Stars
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.28,0:02:15.25,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Aria...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.72,0:02:26.21,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry... oww.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.66,0:02:25.62,DogDays-overlap,N,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.62,0:02:27.00,DogDays-overlap,N,0000,0000,0000,,This will hurt a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.00,0:02:28.52,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I was caught off guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.52,0:02:29.80,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I couldn't do more.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.80,0:02:32.34,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too... I couldn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.71,0:02:35.48,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,They must be pretty good to do
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.48,0:02:37.80,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,this much to Sharl and the chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.80,0:02:39.54,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,It looked like a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.54,0:02:43.46,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,It had human form, but that wasn't human.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.88,0:02:45.39,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,It was a type of demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.74,0:02:47.37,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,A humanoid demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.67,0:02:49.79,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Is there such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.79,0:02:51.77,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,A disciple, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.77,0:02:52.75,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.10,0:02:55.24,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Demons who took the form of
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.24,0:02:57.28,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,humans existed in the distant past.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.58,0:03:00.10,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,They were highly intelligent, \Nwielding power that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.10,0:03:02.48,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,was a manifestation of greed and disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.90,0:03:05.11,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,That must be the Disciple of Illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.43,0:03:08.00,DogDays-main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,We must bring back Aria-dono.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:09.66,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,No, chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.09,0:03:11.71,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,We'll follow him
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.71,0:03:14.47,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,and kick his butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.18,0:03:17.26,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We need to save Aria, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.26,0:03:18.10,DogDays-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.48,0:03:22.42,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,This way. \NI hear the sound this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.42,0:03:24.44,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,The presence is getting stronger, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.44,0:03:25.93,DogDays-overlap,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.31,0:03:35.09,DogDays-overlap,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Leave. Humans... Leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.09,0:03:36.21,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,It talked?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.51,0:03:38.92,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,These things aren't talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.92,0:03:41.07,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,They're just sharing the Disciple's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.07,0:03:43.95,DogDays-overlap,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,You're in Aria's way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.95,0:03:46.24,DogDays-overlap,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.73,0:03:48.83,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Not happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.83,0:03:50.95,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We have something we have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.10,0:03:56.57,DogDays-overlap,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.57,0:04:00.21,DogDays-overlap,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one I can least forgive!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.15,0:04:03.11,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,There are two princes here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.11,0:04:04.77,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you mean me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.19,0:04:08.10,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to talk, let's talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.53,0:04:10.24,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Aria's safe, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.42,0:04:13.80,DogDays-overlap,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you say
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.80,0:04:17.23,DogDays-overlap,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Aria's name!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.23,0:04:18.61,DogDays-overlap,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.61,0:04:21.57,DogDays-overlap,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have even know \Nwhat the heck's going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.57,0:04:23.74,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Can we calm down and talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.71,0:04:35.25,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.25,0:04:41.76,DogDays-main,J,0000,0000,0000,,Vert, where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.30,0:04:44.56,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear a sound that \Nsounds like his main body.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.56,0:04:45.88,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,I think I can follow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.96,0:04:48.75,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Then leave this to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.75,0:04:51.28,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Vert and the others take \NGaul to the main body!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.28,0:04:53.36,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.65,0:04:55.64,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help Nanami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.78,0:05:03.03,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks! I'll let you guys handle it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:05.74,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.29,0:05:13.79,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Just you wait, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.61,0:05:15.60,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Aria.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.45,0:05:17.35,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Aria.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.06,0:05:19.15,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Aria.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.16,0:05:22.19,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Verde?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.15,0:05:24.16,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Verde...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.93,0:05:26.05,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,it's you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.41,0:05:28.85,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you back your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.24,0:05:33.49,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.40,0:05:36.98,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I remember everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.33,0:05:39.81,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Aria!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.41,0:05:47.00,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotten used to this \Nform now, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.00,0:05:48.16,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.16,0:05:49.76,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm used to it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.76,0:05:51.95,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,And you're with Verde again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.95,0:05:53.05,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.59,0:05:56.94,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,He's strange for a sky person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.94,0:06:00.36,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,He seems strangely human, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.73,0:06:02.14,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't he cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.46,0:06:05.17,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,He's always nice to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.08,0:06:07.65,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Verde?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.32,0:06:16.41,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Aria?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.33,0:06:19.76,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Were you watching the surface again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.06,0:06:22.37,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,J-Just a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.94,0:06:25.64,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,The heroes and the princesses are so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.64,0:06:27.92,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,And there's a wonderful prince, isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.92,0:06:30.07,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's not all, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.37,0:06:31.32,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.72,0:06:34.09,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I like to think about what I'd do
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.09,0:06:37.24,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,if I went to the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.81,0:06:39.83,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,That's fun, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.18,0:06:43.90,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,You can have the same form \Nas a surface person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.90,0:06:45.84,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't you go if you wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.46,0:06:49.19,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Even in this form,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.19,0:06:52.22,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get far from water, \Njust like you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.54,0:06:54.97,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,And this year I was chosen \Nto be the songstress.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.34,0:06:56.56,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I won't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.56,0:06:58.96,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,For the Priestess and the \NStar Whale's sake, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.74,0:07:00.98,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,And for everyone's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.25,0:07:15.99,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,My life in the village is \Nso peaceful and quiet,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.22,0:07:18.95,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,but it's just a little boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.95,0:07:21.50,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,My love for the surface is just a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.45,0:07:26.37,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.77,0:07:35.71,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Someday I'd love to
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.57,0:07:38.10,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,go to the surface...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.17,0:07:40.34,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,It can come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.62,0:07:46.14,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,I'll grant your wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.14,0:07:48.23,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Verde... wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.23,0:07:50.03,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,You can talk now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.88,0:07:54.69,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make your dream come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.69,0:07:57.91,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to the surface and keep \Nit a secret from everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.96,0:08:00.14,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.14,0:08:02.41,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,It would be wonderful \Nif I could go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.41,0:08:05.60,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,If I grant your wish,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.04,0:08:10.05,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,will you sing for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:12.21,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.65,0:08:13.80,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.80,0:08:14.83,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.34,0:08:16.35,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.28,0:08:49.81,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I know where the power to
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.28,0:08:52.51,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,make Aria's dream
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.96,0:08:54.72,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,come true is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.07,0:08:57.14,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,The reason I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.47,0:08:59.22,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,My true form...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.98,0:09:07.55,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make Aria's dream
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.23,0:09:09.66,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.59,0:09:24.58,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can make her dream come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.95,0:09:34.82,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,The Star Whale that locks Aria away...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.82,0:09:38.01,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,The village and priestess \Nthat hold her back...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.85,0:09:42.72,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I can make them all go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.53,0:09:56.60,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.15,0:09:58.89,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,What happened, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.27,0:10:00.20,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Aria.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:03.16,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Verde... Is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.56,0:10:05.99,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,You promised, Aria.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.99,0:10:09.04,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,We'd go to the surface in secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.46,0:10:11.43,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Verde, it's you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.97,0:10:14.80,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,No... this isn't what I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:17.64,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Aria... you promised,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.64,0:10:19.18,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,but you lied?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.44,0:10:20.54,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.29,0:10:22.68,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't lie, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.04,0:10:25.18,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,But this wasn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.16,0:10:27.49,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.49,0:10:32.68,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect your songs and voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.20,0:10:48.56,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.17,0:10:51.50,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,We can go anywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.50,0:10:53.56,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.84,0:11:10.23,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,The Star Whale...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.73,0:11:14.06,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,You're trying to stop me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.08,0:11:36.97,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.22,0:11:39.47,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,I can't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.10,0:11:46.80,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.41,0:11:48.22,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,I have to help them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.29,0:12:04.54,DogDays-overlap,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,Aria...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.12,0:12:06.21,DogDays-overlap,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.21,0:12:09.87,DogDays-overlap,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,Find me... and stay by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.59,0:12:26.27,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.27,0:12:27.35,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,There's a door!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.59,0:12:28.47,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.14,0:12:37.11,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Aria...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.55,0:12:40.60,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Gaul!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.21,0:12:43.11,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.36,0:12:44.49,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Is it you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.29,0:13:18.46,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,My guards are famous for appearing and
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.46,0:13:20.48,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,disappearing when you least expect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.94,0:13:23.74,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,They can chase and run faster than anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.00,0:13:26.16,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Y-You...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.04,0:13:28.32,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get in
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.32,0:13:31.94,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,our way, human!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.64,0:13:36.38,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Just like I thought, you're just a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.67,0:13:40.63,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think you can get by in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.65,0:13:48.94,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Just by being a selfish brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.26,0:13:50.48,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.48,0:13:52.04,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.34,0:13:54.64,DogDays-main,J,0000,0000,0000,,It's our boss's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.17,0:13:56.55,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.08,0:14:00.15,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I made him like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:01.99,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.49,0:14:04.78,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,but you can't handle him anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.06,0:14:09.03,DogDays-main,J,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's a really \Ntroublesome type of demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.57,0:14:13.54,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,If I go back, he'll do what I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.54,0:14:16.22,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,But that would mean
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.22,0:14:18.04,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,we're abandoning you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.79,0:14:22.79,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Our boss wouldn't let that happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.79,0:14:25.25,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,nor would any of our friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.54,0:14:26.55,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.36,0:14:31.62,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Our biggest goal is to save the Star Whale
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.62,0:14:33.56,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,and all the Star People, including you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.41,0:14:37.82,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm also training to be a specialist
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.82,0:14:39.66,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,in dealing with demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.17,0:14:43.87,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he's a Disciple, if he \Ncan be saved, I want to save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.21,0:14:47.03,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,What we need isn't sacrifice and dedication,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:48.98,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,it's information and a plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.38,0:14:51.79,DogDays-main,J,0000,0000,0000,,Would you tell us the details?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.28,0:14:55.51,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What happened between you and him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.12,0:15:04.34,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Aria said she wanted to go to the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.34,0:15:06.59,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to make that dream come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.99,0:15:10.47,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to do this; we'll take her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.93,0:15:22.73,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,If you promise not to be \Nbad, we'll take you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.73,0:15:25.03,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,I won't believe that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.93,0:15:29.64,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,The people of the surface \Nrefuse to accept us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.36,0:15:31.99,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Even in the distant past,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.74,0:15:36.74,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,they tried to exterminate us, \Neven though we didn't do anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.54,0:15:38.50,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.72,0:15:40.06,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,I won't believe in the star people
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.36,0:15:42.97,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,or the humans of the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.42,0:15:46.57,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make them all sleep with my power,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.57,0:15:49.08,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,and make a peaceful and gentle world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.08,0:15:50.63,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.63,0:15:52.01,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,I won't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.79,0:16:04.65,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Once all the humans
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.65,0:16:07.38,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,in our way are gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.73,0:16:11.40,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Aria can go to the surface to play in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.93,0:16:18.75,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,She'll let me be the only \None to hear her songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.59,0:16:21.16,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,So human...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.16,0:16:23.67,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Sleep here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.19,0:16:32.57,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,The Hero Shinku
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.18,0:16:35.68,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,is here in Hero Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.29,0:16:38.86,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get in
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.18,0:16:43.51,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.41,0:16:46.72,DogDays-main,E,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.72,0:16:50.04,DogDays-main,E,0000,0000,0000,,the situation's worse than we imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.34,0:16:53.20,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just have to cut open a path.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.54,0:16:56.05,DogDays-main,Co,0000,0000,0000,,Alliance knights and medics!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.05,0:16:58.16,DogDays-main,Co,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.16,0:16:58.70,DogDays-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.02,0:17:01.48,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Princess, I'm going to up our speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.48,0:17:03.46,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Please do!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.73,0:17:08.12,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.12,0:17:10.77,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,The songstress from the \Nsurface is here, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.29,0:17:13.84,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody, get the dais for \Nthe Star Festival ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.15,0:17:15.09,DogDays-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.00,0:17:17.33,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.78,0:17:19.47,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Pega, this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.22,0:17:24.10,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Your wings may be the key to saving everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.11,0:17:27.40,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Show the dragon priestess \NSharl and everyone else
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:30.33,DogDays-main,F,0000,0000,0000,,your true form.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.10,0:17:42.96,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry princess, to ask you \Nto sing in all this chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.96,0:17:44.38,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.38,0:17:46.85,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,I'll sing anywhere, at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.25,0:17:50.70,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Especially if it can help \Nkeep the Sky Sea safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.70,0:17:53.73,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing that would \Nmake me happier as a singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.64,0:18:01.64,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.61,0:18:11.80,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Princess of Biscotti, Hero Rebecca,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.80,0:18:13.13,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.97,0:18:15.24,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Priestess!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.53,0:18:16.78,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.78,0:18:18.16,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,It's Pega.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.16,0:18:20.06,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,This is his true form.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.04,0:18:24.05,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.42,0:18:28.04,DogDays-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,The star festival will be ready soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.30,0:18:29.29,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.59,0:18:31.77,DogDays-main,E,0000,0000,0000,,Stay sharp!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.77,0:18:33.52,DogDays-main,E,0000,0000,0000,,There's still more!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.52,0:18:34.30,DogDays-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.14,0:18:43.73,DogDays-main,Co,0000,0000,0000,,There's no end to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.62,0:18:48.50,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,No army is infinite.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.50,0:18:49.44,DogDays-main,Co,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.35,0:19:04.33,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Shinku!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.33,0:19:05.83,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Gaul!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.33,0:19:13.34,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Divine Rule: Glorious Flying Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.02,0:19:31.23,DogDays-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.70,0:19:34.48,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.48,0:19:37.21,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,No, this is the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.25,0:19:43.49,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,This song...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.08,0:19:45.43,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's starting...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.39,0:19:48.00,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,The princess' song.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.53,0:21:33.48,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.48,0:21:35.95,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's sing a song of healing \Nto the Star Whale, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.95,0:21:37.12,DogDays-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.54,0:23:32.40,DogDays-main-top,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this wonderful person?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.40,0:23:33.76,DogDays-main-top,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,Who could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.32,0:23:36.48,DogDays-main-top,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,Call me Pegasus Mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.48,0:23:38.46,DogDays-main-top,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Next week's the last episode?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.01,0:23:40.01,DogDays-next-ep-title,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,1)}Returning Home
